<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>AIShop — WhatsApp AI Assistant for Any Business</title>
<style>
  :root{--green:#1f9d55;--green-d:#177a42;--ink:#10241b;--muted:#5b6b63;--bg:#f6faf7;--line:#e3ece7;}
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
  body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);background:var(--bg);line-height:1.5;}
  .nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:18px 24px;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;}
  .brand{font-weight:800;font-size:20px;color:var(--green-d);}
  .brand span{color:var(--ink);}
  .nav a{margin-left:18px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;font-size:14px;}
  .nav a.cta{background:var(--green);color:#fff;padding:9px 16px;border-radius:9px;}
  .hero{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding:64px 24px 40px;}
  .hero h1{font-size:42px;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.5px;}
  .hero h1 em{color:var(--green-d);font-style:normal;}
  .hero p{font-size:18px;color:var(--muted);margin:18px auto 0;max-width:620px;}
  .btns{margin-top:30px;display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .btn{padding:14px 24px;border-radius:11px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--green);color:#fff;}
  .btn-primary:hover{background:var(--green-d);}
  .btn-ghost{background:#fff;color:var(--ink);border:1px solid var(--line);}
  .tag{display:inline-block;background:#e9f7ef;color:var(--green-d);font-weight:700;font-size:12px;padding:6px 12px;border-radius:999px;margin-bottom:18px;}
  .grid{max-width:1000px;margin:30px auto 0;padding:0 24px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:18px;}
  .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:24px;}
  .card h3{font-size:17px;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .card p{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;}
  .ico{font-size:26px;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .types{max-width:1000px;margin:40px auto 0;padding:0 24px;text-align:center;}
  .types h2{font-size:26px;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .types .sub{color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:22px;}
  .chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;justify-content:center;}
  .chip{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:999px;padding:10px 18px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;}
  .band{max-width:760px;margin:56px auto;padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;background:#10241b;color:#fff;border-radius:20px;}
  .band h2{font-size:26px;}
  .band p{color:#c7d6cd;margin:10px 0 22px;}
  .band .btn-primary{background:var(--green);}
  footer{text-align:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px;padding:30px;}
  @media(max-width:600px){.hero h1{font-size:32px;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="nav">
    <div class="brand">AI<span>Shop</span></div>
    <div>
      <a href="admin.html">Admin</a>
      <a class="cta" href="app.html">Get started</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="hero">
    <span class="tag">WhatsApp AI · Arabic + English</span>
    <h1>Turn WhatsApp into your <em>24/7 AI assistant</em></h1>
    <p>AIShop answers customers, takes orders, books appointments, and saves
       everything automatically — for grocery shops, pharmacies, restaurants,
       clinics, and more. No app to install. It just works on WhatsApp.</p>
    <div class="btns">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="app.html">Onboard your business →</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="admin.html">Admin dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="card"><div class="ico">🛒</div><h3>Takes orders</h3>
      <p>Customers chat naturally; the assistant builds the cart, calculates totals, collects the address, and saves the order.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="ico">📅</div><h3>Books appointments</h3>
      <p>For clinics & hospitals: collects patient details, offers available slots, and confirms the booking with an ID.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="ico">🌐</div><h3>Arabic & English</h3>
      <p>Detects each customer's language and replies in it — no mixing, no switching.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="ico">🙋</div><h3>Escalates to humans</h3>
      <p>Complaints or "I want a manager" are routed straight to your team.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="ico">🧠</div><h3>Remembers customers</h3>
      <p>Saves delivery addresses and details so repeat customers are served faster.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="ico">⚡</div><h3>Live in minutes</h3>
      <p>Fill one form, connect your WhatsApp number, and your assistant is online.</p></div>
  </section>

  <section class="types">
    <h2>Built for any business</h2>
    <p class="sub">One platform, tailored automatically to your business type.</p>
    <div class="chips">
      <span class="chip">Baqala / Grocery</span><span class="chip">Supermarket</span>
      <span class="chip">Pharmacy</span><span class="chip">Restaurant</span>
      <span class="chip">Cafeteria</span><span class="chip">Clinic</span>
      <span class="chip">Hospital</span><span class="chip">Retail</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <h2>Ready to go live?</h2>
    <p>Set up your WhatsApp AI assistant in a few minutes.</p>
    <a class="btn btn-primary" href="app.html">Onboard your business →</a>
  </section>

  <footer>© <span id="y"></span> AIShop · Powered by WhatsApp AI</footer>
  <script>document.getElementById("y").textContent=new Date().getFullYear();</script>
</body>
</html>
